# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:9
translate french counselorconversation3_535998b2:

    # pc "There's this girl that lives next door to me, Jamie."
    pc "Il y a cette fille qui habite à côté de chez moi, Jamie."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:10
translate french counselorconversation3_dcfcdfa2:

    # pc "I can't get her out of my mind."
    pc "Je n’arrive pas à la sortir de ma tête."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:11
translate french counselorconversation3_bee654f7:

    # sc "You like her?"
    sc "Tu l'aimes bien ?"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:12
translate french counselorconversation3_abd0877e:

    # pc "Yeah, but there's more to it than that."
    pc "Ouais, mais c'est plus que ça."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:13
translate french counselorconversation3_c5ac6fea:

    # pc "We have a history. We dated when we were younger, but then I hurt her."
    pc "On a un passé ensemble. On est sortis ensemble quand on était plus jeunes, mais ensuite je lui ai fait du mal."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:14
translate french counselorconversation3_3b37105b:

    # pc "I didn't mean to, but I did."
    pc "Je ne voulais pas, mais je l'ai fait."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:15
translate french counselorconversation3_83b99294:

    # pc "Then I left, and now that I'm back it's sort of like we're starting over, but we still have all this history."
    pc "Puis je suis parti, et maintenant que je suis de retour, c'est un peu comme si on repartait à zéro, mais on a toujours tout ce passé."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:18
translate french counselorconversation3_af5378b6:

    # pc "Do you know what I mean?"
    pc "Tu vois ce que je veux dire ?"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:19
translate french counselorconversation3_eec64a34:

    # sc "I think I do. You have memories with her, but it's almost like it's a different person because it's been so long."
    sc "Je crois que oui. Tu as des souvenirs avec elle, mais c'est presque comme si c'était une autre personne parce que ça fait si longtemps."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:20
translate french counselorconversation3_de5061cc:

    # pc "Exactly! I remember hanging out with her when we were younger, but both of us have changed so much it's sort of like remembering a movie."
    pc "Exactement ! Je me souviens de nos moments ensemble quand on était plus jeunes, mais on a tellement changé tous les deux que c'est un peu comme se souvenir d'un film."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:21
translate french counselorconversation3_a7dabb45:

    # sc "Does it bother you?"
    sc "Ça te dérange ?"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:22
translate french counselorconversation3_72e3f009:

    # pc "No, not at all."
    pc "Non, pas du tout."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:23
translate french counselorconversation3_65acc085:

    # pc "It's nice actually. It's like we have a head start."
    pc "C'est plutôt sympa, en fait. C'est comme si on avait une longueur d'avance."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:24
translate french counselorconversation3_46d1797b:

    # pc "What happened before isn't holding our relationship back at all. It's really like we just skipped the first couple of levels, you know? Because we already did them."
    pc "Ce qui s'est passé avant ne freine pas du tout notre relation. C'est vraiment comme si on avait sauté les deux premiers niveaux, tu vois ? Parce qu'on les a déjà franchis."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:25
translate french counselorconversation3_abd28437:

    # sc "So things are getting serious with her?"
    sc "Alors, ça devient sérieux avec elle ?"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:26
translate french counselorconversation3_ee1883b8:

    # pc "I don't know if I'd call it serious, but we both like each other."
    pc "Je ne sais pas si j'appellerais ça « sérieux », mais on s'apprécie tous les deux."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:27
translate french counselorconversation3_d72f2f51:

    # sc "Companionship is good. You should have somebody in your life that you can rely on."
    sc "C'est bien d'avoir de la compagnie. Tu devrais avoir quelqu'un dans ta vie sur qui tu peux compter."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:28
translate french counselorconversation3_7d69eb5d:

    # sc "Somebody who makes you happy."
    sc "Quelqu'un qui te rend heureuse."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:30
translate french counselorconversation3_1487ed22:

    # "Her voice suddenly takes on a somber tone as she says this, as if she does not have that someone."
    "Sa voix prend soudain un ton sombre lorsqu'elle dit cela, comme si elle n'avait pas cette personne."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:31
translate french counselorconversation3_5d687698:

    # "But you've seen the ring on her finger, you know that she's married."
    "Mais tu as vu la bague à son doigt, tu sais qu'elle est mariée."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:35
translate french counselorconversation3_3c7fbaef:

    # sc "Oh, yes I'm fine."
    sc "Oh, oui, ça va."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:39
translate french counselorconversation3_fa2bc12a:

    # sc "Good, I'm happy for you."
    sc "Bien, je suis contente pour toi."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:41
translate french counselorconversation3_fc38e4d4:

    # sc "Well it's about time for you to get to class."
    sc "Bon, il est temps que tu ailles en cours."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:42
translate french counselorconversation3_a8c43555:

    # pc "Okay, I'll see you next time Gertrude."
    pc "D'accord, à la prochaine, Gertrude."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:43
translate french counselorconversation3_1b784c07:

    # sc "Bye, [pcname]."
    sc "Au revoir, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/3 - Jamie.rpy:44
translate french counselorconversation3_e4b88e88:

    # "With that, I stand up and head to class."
    "Sur ce, je me lève et me dirige vers la classe."

